ZaykaExpress
ZaykaExpress is a food delivery web application inspired by Swiggy, designed to provide a seamless food ordering experience with real-time restaurant listings, menu browsing, and order placement.

Features
ğŸ” Restaurant Listings: Fetch and display nearby restaurants.
ğŸ“œ Menu Display: View restaurant menus with item details.
ğŸ” Search Functionality: Search restaurants based on location.
âš¡ Shimmer Effect: Smooth UI with loading placeholders.
ğŸŒ Routing with React Router: Seamless page navigation.
ğŸ“¦ State Management: Using Redux Toolkit for global state handling.
ğŸ¨ Tailwind CSS: Modern, responsive UI styling.
Tech Stack
Frontend: React, React Router, Redux Toolkit
Styling: Tailwind CSS
APIs: Swiggy Unofficial API (via proxy)
Icons & Fonts: FontAwesome, React Icons
Installation & Setup
Clone the repository:
git clone https://github.com/yourusername/mealrush.git
cd mealrush
Install dependencies:
npm install
Start the development server:
npm start
Open the app in your browser at http://localhost:3000.
